OL,3,CCouncil chief 'proud' of empty #50m
OL,4,Cmusic venue
OL,6,FThe leader of Bradford Council says
OL,7,Fshe is "really proud" of a #50m music
OL,8,Fvenue which is currently lying empty
OL,9,Fafter the operator pulled out.
OL,11,FQuestions about the future of Bradford
OL,12,FLive have intensified since the
OL,13,Fcouncil confirmed last week, following
OL,14,Fmonths of speculation, that NEC Group
OL,15,Fwould no longer be involved.
OL,17,FSusan Hinchcliffe insisted the venue -
OL,18,Fwhich should have opened in November -
OL,19,Fwould launch in 2025, during
OL,20,FBradford's year as UK City of Culture.
