OL,6,FShe said "a number of operators" were
OL,7,Finterested in taking over the
OL,8,Fmanagement of the 3,800-seater venue,
OL,9,Fwhich is built on the site of the
OL,10,Fcity's old Odeon cinema.
OL,12,FBut she declined to say how many due
OL,13,Fto "commercial sensitivities".
OL,15,FAnswering questions for the first time
OL,16,Fsince last week's announcement, she
OL,17,Fsaid: "We're really proud of this
OL,18,Fvenue. People can see the future that
OL,19,Fit represents.
