OL,3,CCouncil chief 'proud' of empty #50m
OL,4,Cmusic venue
OL,6,F"Everyone's really looking forward to
OL,7,Fgetting in here I know that and we're
OL,8,Freally looking forward to opening it
OL,9,Fup for everybody.
OL,11,F"We now know that during 2025 it will
OL,12,Fopen, people will be able to enjoy it
OL,13,Fas part of City of Culture. We know
OL,14,Fthis is the right thing to do as part
OL,15,Fof our regeneration across the
OL,16,Fdistrict."
OL,18,FBradford Live was initially forecast
OL,19,Fto cost between #22m and #25m, but
OL,20,Fcosts spiralled, with the council
OL,21,Fputting in #44m.
