OL,6,FThe rest came from the West Yorkshire
OL,7,FCombined Authority (WYCA), the
OL,8,Fgovernment and the Heritage Lottery
OL,9,FFund.
OL,11,FA full refurbishment was effectively
OL,12,Fcompleted in July.
OL,14,FEarlier this year, it was announced
OL,15,Fthat two events ` an Abba tribute act
OL,16,Fand a show of Bob Marley songs ` would
OL,17,Flaunch the venue in November.
OL,19,FBut those were cancelled and the
OL,20,Fofficial website has now been
OL,21,Feffectively dismantled.
