OL,6,FThe council said the NEC Group had
OL,7,Fpulled out "following a strategic
OL,8,Freview of its business" and wanted to
OL,9,Ffocus on its Birmingham operation.
OL,11,FThe authority, which earlier this year
OL,12,Fapproved #40m of spending cuts amid
OL,13,Fhuge financial problems, has faced
OL,14,Fcriticism for spending #44m of
OL,15,Ftaxpayers' money on the project.
OL,17,FBut Ms Hinchcliffe insisted it was the
OL,18,Fright decision.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
