OL,3,CCouncil chief 'proud' of empty #50m
OL,4,Cmusic venue
OL,6,F"This will be a great asset and I am
OL,7,Fconfident that in a year or two's time
OL,8,Fpeople will look back on this and see
OL,9,Fhow magnificent it is and see how well
OL,10,Fit serves the Bradford economy.
OL,12,F"Nothing is ever easy, I don't expect
OL,13,Fthings to be easy in life. We're
OL,14,Fpushing forward on our regeneration
OL,15,Fand growth ambitions."
OL,17,FShe added: "We have to spend on
OL,18,Fregeneration for growth. Without
OL,19,Fgrowth we have no future as a city."
